Cell["\<\
The Hadamard Test is a quantum algorithm used to estimate the expectation \
value of a unitary operator with respect to a given quantum state. It plays a \
crucial role in quantum computing, particularly in the context of variational \
quantum algorithms and quantum phase estimation.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->383184099,ExpressionUUID->"3a6db4f7-4fca-4c28-9bff-dc19f3e32cb0"],

